Package model

Class Inventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Inventory
  • public class Inventory
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds lists of available parts and products in inventory system. Static methods allow universal access to contents for sharing data.
    Author:
    Brian Schwemmer
